n:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho bi\u1ebft HAGL c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng sau khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 V-League 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng sau c\u00fa va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 6 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luong Xuan Truong khong lo HAGL bi suy yeu vi thieu Tuan Anh hinh anh\" title=\"L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng lo HAGL b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu Tu\u1ea5n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/_27a3098-1757.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\u00a0kh\u00f4ng lo HAGL b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu Tu\u1ea5n Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t HAGL nh\u01b0 Tu\u1ea5n Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, tuy nhi\u00ean Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng lo ng\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB HAGL L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNgay \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a HAGL. T\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n trong ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin BHL CLB HAGL lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng thay th\u1ebf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 CLB s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y\u201d, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2018h\u00edp\u2019 chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i HAGL sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup g\u1eb7p Jordan. Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i d\u00e0i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u.\u00a0 Tuy nhi\u00ean Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa CLB HAGL vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay 1/4. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"vong 4 V-League 2018\" title=\"v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/vong-4-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>LT\u0110\u00a0v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\nRoboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"674","checkdouble":"183272"},{"date":"06:09 01/04","title":"N\u00d3NG: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/10/nong-tien-ve-quang-hai-se-sang-nhat-ban-thi-dau-voi-hop-dong-3-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3