2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Monaco trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p, PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/xdedo.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nPSG b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa \u201c\u0103n ba\u201d qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i sau khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 bay kh\u1ecfi Champions League. HLV Unai Emery ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u0169i \u0111inh ba Di Maria \u2013 Cavani \u2013 Mbappe l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, AS Monaco c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Falcao hay \u201cng\u00f2i n\u1ed5\u201d Lemar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i s\u1edbm gi\u00fap PSG gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Khi hi\u1ec7p 1 ch\u01b0a tr\u00f4i qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5, Mbappe c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u1ed9c di\u1ec5n solo qua t\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Glik c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Sau h\u01a1n 2 ph\u00fat tham kh\u1ea3o VAR, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0 Cavani kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 21, Mbappe l\u1ea1i ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n x\u00e9 toang h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Monaco cho Di Maria tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng. \u201cThi\u00ean th\u1ea7n\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Subasic n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 b\u1eb1ng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua PSG vs Monaco 3-0 chung ket cup lien doan phap 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 PSG vs Monaco 3-0 chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n ph\u00e1p 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/ivwynmluffnu73edv8bg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1, Falcao \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Trapp nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn khi x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a VAR. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, PSG c\u0169ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Cavani v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, PSG v\u1eabn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Mbappe \u201cch\u1ed1t h\u1ea1\u201d ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng pha t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c r\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Cavani d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-0 \u1edf ph\u00fat 85.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Monaco kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Malmut Atlantique c\u1ee7a Bordeaux, PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 8 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf t\u00fai ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia Ph\u00e1p. M\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u201c\u0103n ba\u201d qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i n\u1eefa \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi HLV Emery v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. <br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u:<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPSG: Trapp, Alves, Kimpembe, Thiago Silva, Berchiche, Verratti (Lo Celso, 70\u2019), Rabiot, Draxler (Diarra, 81\u2019), Mbappe, Cavani, Di Maria (Pastore, 52\u2019).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMonaco: Subasic, Sidibe, Glik, Jemerson, Raggi, Moutinho (Ghezzal, 80\u2019), Tielemans (Jovetic, 46\u2019), Fabinho, Lopes (Diakhaby, 73\u2019), Falcao, Lemar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"672","checkdouble":"183277"},{"date":"02:19 01/04","title":"Bayern Munich 6-0 Dortmund: Der Klassiker qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/bayern-munich-60-dortmund-der-klassiker-qua-chenh-lech.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-s