tps://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/las-palmas-vs-real-madrid.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><strong>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thang Las Palmas 3-0\" title=\"Real Madrid thang Las Palmas 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Real-Madrid-thang-Las-Palmas-3-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real Madrid th\u1eafng Las Palmas 3-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong> </strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League v\u1edbi Juventus gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n sau, HLV Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Real Madrid. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng Cristiano Ronaldo, Toni Kroos hay Sergio Ramos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch Las Palmas vs Real Madrid t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 30 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi Las Palmas, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3 \u0111\u1ed9i &ldquo;c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; t\u1ea1i La Liga. B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Karim Benzema r\u1ed3i Marco Asensio \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Chichizola c\u1ee7a Las Palmas ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3. \u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf ph\u00fat 26 khi Gareth Bale k\u1ebft th\u00fac th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng nhanh c\u1ee7a Real, m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Real:</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/las-palmas-vs-real-phut-26.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Las Palmas. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n t\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a Real. Trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Gran Canaria c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Jonathan Calleri ph\u00fat 39. Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, Benzema kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn 2-0 cho Los Blancos v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Benzema nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/las-palmas-vs-real-phut-39.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal v\u1eabn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ea7y v\u0169 b\u00e3o. Pha b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh v\u00e0 b\u1ecb k\u00ea ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Madrid th\u00eam m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ch\u00ednh tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Real v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Las Palmas 3-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 c\u1ee7a Bale:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/las-palmas-vs-real-phut-51.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n trong tay, Real ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus sau \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i ung dung nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m. N\u1ebfu Bale v\u00e0 Benzema ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng 3-0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Las Palmas. H\u1ecd thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Deportivo r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 2 (2/4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH XU\u1ea4T&nbsp;PH\u00c1T:<br>\r\nLas Palmas:</strong> Leandro Chichizola; Michel Macedo, Ximo Navarro, Alejandro Galvez, Matias Aguirregaray; Javi Castellano, Vicente Gomez; Alen Halilovic, Alberto Aquilani, Momo; Jonathan Calleri.<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 b\u1ecb: Raul Lizoain, Benito Ramirez, Jairo Samperio, David Garcia, Imoh Ezekiel, David Simon.<br>\r\n<strong>Real Madrid: </strong>Keylor Navas; Nacho, Jesus Vallejo, Raphael Varane, Theo Hernandez; Lucas Vazquez, Casemiro, Luka Modric, Marco Asensio; Karim Benzema, Gareth Bale.<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 b\u1ecb: Kiko Casilla, Mateo Kovacic, Marcos Llorente, Alvaro Tejero, Borja Mayoral, Oscar Rodriguez, Achraf Hakimi.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nG.V (Bongda24h.vn) <br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"670","checkdouble":"183240"},{"date":"02:40 01/04","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Sevilla vs Barca tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 30 La Liga 2017/18","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/30/ket-qua-sevilla-vs-barca-tran-dau-vong-30-la-liga-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-fu