Sevilla t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 30 La Liga m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0110TQG v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Ramon Sanchez Pizjuan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Barca. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Luis Suarez ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 khi Sevilla m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 xem \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean v\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sevilla t\u1ea1o ra. Nh\u1eefng Joaquin Correa, Luis Muriel hay Franco Vazquez&hellip; \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd sau c\u00f9ng. R\u1ed3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 36, r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c Barca c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t khi Correa c\u0103ng ngang d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 cho Vazquez m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Sevilla c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u00fat 36 c\u1ee7a Sevilla:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/sevilla-vs-barca-phut-36.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u1eabn nghi\u00eang nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Sevilla. H\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng phong t\u1ecfa m\u1ecdi ng\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng nhanh l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n5 ph\u00fat sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, Muriel nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u pha b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Sevilla b\u1ecf qua v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m n\u01a1i 1/3 cu\u1ed1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 c\u1ee7a Sevilla:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/sevilla-vs-barca-phut-50.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00fat 88, Sevilla v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eabn Barca 2-0. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng c\u00f3 2 ph\u00fat 88 v\u00e0 89 ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i th\u00f4i, ai ng\u1edd Barca l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c m\u1edbi c\u00f3 trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Luis Suarez r\u1ed3i Lionel Messi (v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ph\u00fat 58) ghi 2 b\u00e0n gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Barca. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc cho Sevilla song c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 88 v\u00e0 89 c\u1ee7a Barca:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/sevilla-vs-barca-phut-88.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/sevilla-vs-barca-phut-89.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nSevilla XI (4-2-3-1):</strong> Rico; Mercado (Layun 46'), Kjaer, Lenglet, Escudero; N'Zonzi, Banega; Navas (Nolito 81'), Vazquez, Correa (Pizarro 72'); Muriel.<br>\r\n<strong>Barcelona XI (4-3-3):</strong> Stegen; Roberto, Pique, Umtiti, Alba; Paulinho (Suarez 77'), Rakitic, Iniesta (Alcacer 81'); Dembele (Messi 58'), Luis Suarez, Coutinho.&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nG.V (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"669","checkdouble":"183252"},{"date":"03:21 01/04","title":"Xem nh\u1eb9 c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 100 b\u00e0n, Lukaku quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/1/xem-nhe-cot-moc-100-ban-lukaku-quyet-gianh-danh-h