se{background-position:-80px -208px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-vertical{background-position:0 -224px}.ui-icon-grip-dotted-horizontal{background-position:-16px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-vertical{background-position:-32px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-solid-horizontal{background-position:-48px -224px}.ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Jose Mourinho r\u1eddi Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u00e0o</strong> \u0111\u00f3n Swansea City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford, Man United \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2-0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1eeda ng\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c: Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t xin t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV\u00a0Jose Mourinho r\u1eddi MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1eeb th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho t\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u00f4ng ra \u0111i l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Soc HLV Jose Mourinho roi MU mot cach dot ngot hinh anh\" title=\"S\u1ed1c HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1eddi MU m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/soc-hlv-jose-mourinho-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c HLV\u00a0M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1eebng</strong> chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, C\u0110V M.U \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ed9p \u0111\u01a1n xin t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u00f3ng m\u1eaft\u201d v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a Mourinho t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 s\u1edf d\u0129 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a sa th\u1ea3i \u00f4ng l\u00e0 b\u1edfi kho\u1ea3n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng cho b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m (k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m) l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u00e0y</strong> \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t xu b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u00fat lui. Nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, M.U v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 sau 20 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00e1</strong> t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f2n l\u1ea1 v\u00e0 n\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea. Trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n ng\u00e1n. Ch\u1ec9 t\u1edbi n\u1eeda hi\u1ec7p 2, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 l\u0169 l\u01b0\u1ee3t ra v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho v\u1ebb m\u1eb7t cau c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c vang l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho chiu nhieu chi trich\" title=\"Mourinho chiu nhieu chi trich\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Mourinho-chiu-nhieu-chi-trich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1eddi MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00e1ng</strong> 3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn M.U c\u00f3 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 sau 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 Sevilla ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u uy t\u00edn. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw, \u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u01b0</strong> ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Pogba, Shaw \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Swansea, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng la \u00f3 v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i M.U ngay t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt m\u1ec9a mai t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Pogba. Cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i co quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa Mou v\u00e0 c\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBa m\u00e1u s\u00e1u c\u01a1n, Mourinho b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1eadt d\u1eady b\u1ecf d\u1edf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi \u0111i, \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d c\u00f2n h\u00e9t l\u1edbn: Kh\u1ed1n ki\u1ebfp! \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c so\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n xin t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c g\u1eedi l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mourinho thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh. H\u1ecd g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac \u00f4ng may m\u1eafn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Nh\u1eefng Carlo Ancelotti, Luis Enrique r\u1ed3i Thomas Tuchel (\u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7) l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t thay th\u1ebf Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"lanh dao M.U Woodward va Mourinho\" title=\"lanh dao M.U Woodward va Mou