x; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Everton, Man City l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn hai l\u1ea7n.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Man Utd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh s\u1edbm 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City lap ky luc sau tran thang Everton.\" title=\"Man City l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Everton.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/man-city-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-sau-tran-thang-everton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Man City l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Everton.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-everton-vs-man-city-23h30-ngay-313-premier-league-201718-372-183228.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Everton</span></span> c\u0169ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn lao. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Man City l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Pep v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 13 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u0169 12 tr\u1eadn do ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng l\u1eadp m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi Kevin Keegan m\u00f9a 2001-02.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City ch\u1ea1m t\u1edbi l\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Premier League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea m\u00f9a 2006-07 v\u00e0 Man Utd m\u00f9a 2012-13 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ri\u00eang Pep Guardiola, ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 50 t\u1ea1i Premier League sau 69 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pep Guardiola tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c hay k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Sau tr\u1eadn, Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Man City s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h45 (5/4) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Everton vs Man City\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Everton vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Everton-vs-Man-City.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Everton vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Everton 1-3 Man City:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_264985\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/01/highlight-everton-vs-man-city-vong-32-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"665","checkdouble":"183267"},{"date":"07:16 01/04","title":"Arsenal vs Stoke (19h30 ng\u00e0y 01/04): Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eeda h\u1eadn","