1eadn khi\u1ebfn HLV Wenger ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Arsenal c\u0169ng xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd ghi 8 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n. Nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal</strong></span> duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Top 4 Premier League v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal vs Stoke (19h30 ngay 0104) Quyet tam rua han hinh anh\" title=\"Arsenal vs Stoke (19h30 ng\u00e0y 0104) Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eeda h\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Arsenal-vs-Stoke-(19h30-ngay-0104)-Quyet-tam-rua-han-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Arsenal \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Ozil, Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Aubameyang. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Ozil thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n. 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ebfn 13 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, trong \u0111\u00f3 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00f4ng 2018: Aubameyang v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Tottenham t\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 san l\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi Chelsea ngay sau \u0111\u00f3. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Europa League.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Arsenal vs Stoke\" title=\"Preview Arsenal vs Stoke\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/30/Preview-Arsenal-vs-Stoke.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal vs Stoke t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 22 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Aaron Ramsey, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/mesut-ozil-43842.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mesut Ozil</strong></span> v\u00e0 Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Alexandre Lacazette v\u00e0 Sead Kolasinac c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Stoke v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Stoke \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Arsenal \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Stoke kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 19 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m an to\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, song v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stoke City dang lam vao tinh canh nguy nan\" title=\"Stoke City dang lam vao tinh canh nguy nan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Stoke-City-dang-lam-vao-tinh-canh-nguy-nan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stoke City \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Stoke l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, 5 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 3 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Stoke h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Arsenal khi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Stephen Ireland, Lee Grant, Choupo-Moting, Mame Biram Diouf, Kevin Wimmer v\u00e0 Ibrahim Afellay \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Charlie Adam b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Stoke City \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Arsenal v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0, Jese l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Paul Lambert.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e2n Emirates l\u00e0 n\u01a1i d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Stoke. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 th\u00e1ng 8/1981, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 37 n\u0103m. Khi m\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 s\u1ebd n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 11.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y Stoke v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng s\u1ebd hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nhen nh\u00f3m hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Top 4 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CSKA Moscow v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Arsenal (4-2-3-1):&nbsp;</strong>33.Cech; 24.Bellerin, 20.Mustafi, 6.Koscielny, 18.Monreal; 8.Ramsey, 29.Xhaka; 7.Mkhitaryan, 11.Ozil, 17.Iwobi, 14.Aubameyang</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Stoke City (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Butland; 8.Johnson, 17.Shawcross, 6.Zouma, 21.Stafylidis; 24.Fletcher, 27.Ndiaye; 22.Shaqiri, 4.Allen, 32.Sobhi; 25.Crouch\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Arsenal vs Stoke\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Stoke\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/1/Arsenal-vs-Stoke-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Stoke</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"664","checkdouble":"183281"},{"date":"22:24 31/03","title":"Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Mane may m\u1eafn tho\u00e1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/klopp-thua-nhan-mane-may-man-thoat-the-do-truoc-palace.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-