om-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Sadio Mane \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp thua nhan Mane may man thoat the do truoc Palace hinh anh\" title=\"Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Mane may m\u1eafn tho\u00e1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/klopp-thua-nhan-mane-may-man-thoat-the-do-truoc-palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mane \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00ec l\u1ed7i ng\u00e3 v\u1edd. Sang hi\u1ec7p hai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 Mane b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Palace \u0111\u1ed1n ng\u00e3. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Mane \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u00f4m b\u00f3ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng\u00a0 t\u00e0i Swarbrick c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb s\u0103m soi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi Mane ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Mane s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec d\u00f9ng tay ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\u201d, Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean k\u00eanh BBC sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Klopp c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi Mane b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u00f2n Liverpool th\u00ec b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty trong 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo quan s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t penalty. Mane \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u01a1i ch\u1eadm m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. V\u1edbi va ch\u1ea1m \u1edf m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u00e3 v\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cXoay quanh Mane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1 t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1edbi 80 ph\u00fat b\u1ecb la \u00f3 li\u1ec1n. H\u00f4m nay r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-172-183245.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-172-183245.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e0 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Adam Lallana \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp xem ch\u1eebng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"663","checkdouble":"183244"},{"date":"22:22 31/03","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/31/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;backg