7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 679 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1ecd trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace vs Liverpool, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp \u1edf 21 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c nhau trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 Premier League, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i (b\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo m\u00f9a 2007/08 v\u00e0 Robin van Persie m\u00f9a 2012/13).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Salah \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (29 b\u00e0n, 9 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung thong ke an tuong sau tran Crystal Palace vs Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace vs Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace vs Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Con s\u1ed1 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 38 b\u00e0n n\u00f3i tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a Salah l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau Luis Suarez m\u00f9a 2013/14 (43). <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Crystal Palace l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua t\u1edbi trong 10 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng (88 vs Tottenham, 90 vs Man Utd v\u00e0 84 vs Liverpool).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sadio Mane tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Demba Ba (43).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 5 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb khi Adam Lallana v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roberto Firmino \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace (6), nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ea3 penalty t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u01a1n Wilfried Zaha (4, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Dominic Calvert-Lewin v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling).<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_264944\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/03/31/highlight-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-32-nha-full.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiep-tuc-no-sung-salah-can-bang-ky-luc-cua-ronaldo-va-van-persie-172-183243.html\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, Salah c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 Van Persie</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp-172-183242.html\">Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool: 90 ph\u00fat nh\u1edb \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u201cThe Klopp\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-crystal-palace-12-liverpool-vong-32-premier-league-201718-326-183239.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-vong-32-premier-league-201718-172-183225.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Crystal Palace vs Liverpool tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-18h30-ngay-313-premier-league-201718-372-183214.html\">Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool (KT): Si\u00ea