1ef1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng 30 Serie A, Roma ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Renato Dall'Ara c\u1ee7a Bologna. HLV Eusebio Di Francesco c\u1ee7a Giallorossi \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn khi c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Edin Dzeko tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u1ee7i ro v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat 17, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c: Radja Nainggolan c\u1ee7a Roma ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u00f4m \u0111\u00f9i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Gerson. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Nainggolan t\u1eadp t\u1ec5nh ra ngh\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f9i ng\u00f9i cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V Roma. Su\u1ed1t v\u00e0i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng qua, anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u201cl\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i\u201d \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona nhan tin Radja Nainggolan cua Roma chan thuong hinh anh\" title=\"Barcelona nh\u1eadn tin Radja Nainggolan c\u1ee7a Roma ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/barcelona-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-radja-nainggolan-cua-roma-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Radja Nainggolan c\u1ee7a Roma ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Nainggolan t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Roma. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua con s\u1ed1 3 b\u00e0n, 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 sau 24 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Nainggolan c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Barcelona t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 5 tu\u1ea7n sau khi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Roma. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Cengiz Under, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i khi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Nainggolan, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Under k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c cho chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u1ee7a Barca c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. Thi\u1ebfu h\u1ecd, Roma \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bologna t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 30 Serie A. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 18 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1edd pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Dzeko v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 AS Roma tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/radja-nainggolan-khong-den-chelsea-va-inter-176-183160.html\">Sao Roma ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Inter v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-y-khang-dinh-roma-khong-so-barca-184-183089.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-cdv-nha-chi-trich-vi-ban-salah-as-roma-noi-gi-172-183027.html\">B\u1ecb C\u0110V nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec b\u00e1n Salah, AS Roma n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/liverpool-va-real-nhan-tin-mung-vu-thu-mon-cua-roma-180-182742.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Real nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/taffarel-khen-thu-mon-alisson-hon-buffon-vi-dai-180-182685.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Buffon v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barcelona-vs-as-roma-tai-tu-ket-champions-league-bay-soi-run-ray-184-182205.html\">Barcelona vs AS Roma t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League: B\u1ea7y s\u00f3i run r\u1ea9y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"660","checkdouble":"183237"},{"date":"18:16 31/03","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Las Palmas vs Real Madrid 23h30 ng\u00e0y 31/1 (La Liga 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/30/truc-tiep-las-palmas-vs-real-madrid-23h30-ngay-311-la-liga-201718.png","ne